Text.string: Ugh! These films are just terrible.

You are just the person I didn't know I wanted to see until I did see you there. Would you like to look through the garbages for my ECHO device? I have lots of money for some reason, and I will give you bunch of it if you help me.
Set up my movies now, okay? We are on edge of greatness here, my friend!
I finally can be able to tell my parents I am famous film man! Ah-hahaha... action! Now come back for your bunches of money!
Oh no! This is terrible. The projector bulb broken now! You have to fix this thing. And I will give you more money bunches to do it too.
The jerk who run this place is called Rohner. He trashed my ECHO because he did not understand my cinematic vision. Even though it's a really great vision.
They're messing with my projector! I'm gonna pull the bleedin' lookyballs outta whoever did this! Go track 'em down, you rabble!
The Gospel of the Calypsos will never be silenced!
Ahahahaha... good riddance! Now go find his bulb stash. My destiny is becoming impatient!
You know what to doooo!||—And if you don't: go replace that bulb!
YES! Bring to me my inevitable fame, Vault Hunter!
I punch Troy in my dreams.
I will disembowel Troy before the hunt is over.
Troy? Screw that cod-swabber!
Messing with Troy? I'm in.

I will be famous now for a thousand millions of years thanks to you, Vault Hunter. I can never repay you, but I will try with all of these bunches of money I am now giving to you. Now if you'll excuse me, I have to practice my acceptance speech.
I want to thank the entire academy for this award for the best filmmaker in universe forever. This is a great honor I am totally deserving of.
Oh hi, Vault Hunter.
But Rohner prefers only these terrible movies this Troy person make.
Oh. Okay.
There are no bulbs in there? Uhhnnnhhh... I'm thinking I saw that jerk Rohner using bulbs for target shooting. Go do target shooting at HIM until he is dying.
You are the best, Vault Hunter. Well, after me. So you are second-best, which is still pretty good.

My films are, without doubting, the highest quality cinematic excellence, and I recommend you all watch them and enjoy them and learn from that. It is about passion, and doing what you love, and then everyone will love you with a lot of passion, see? If you're me, anyway.

All you have to do is follow your dreaming. I followed my dreaming, and, it brought me this. The award for best filmmaker in universe forever. Maybe if you follow your dreaming you can do that too. Except for I already did it and it's forever so, good luck with that.
Where am I, really?
What is really real?
They carry me like angels.
If I fall, will you catch me?
It's not in that one! Keep looking!
I keep running, really fast.
Oh, hi, me.
It end like this. Weird, right?
I always hate... me?
It's not in that one either. Oh, no!
That's it! That's really good working! You are almost as amazing as myself! Now it's time to put my movie on the big screen! That one. Go plug into the movie shooter, okay?
No go in door! Do go die!
